WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

01:25.561 --> 01:31.392
【The fate that cannot be liberated】

01:31.392 --> 01:34.368
[Episode 18]

01:41.560 --> 01:43.619
It would be better if Hong Zao was here

01:43.619 --> 01:45.239
You can keep each other company.

01:51.159 --> 01:52.580
This horse is very obedient.

01:52.580 --> 01:53.760
Tomorrow I will teach you how to ride...

01:58.080 --> 01:59.136
sorry.

01:59.680 --> 02:01.040
I'm not the person you want to see

02:01.920 --> 02:03.480
Why come if you know you're not welcome?

02:04.480 --> 02:06.319
Do you think I'm deaf and blind and
don't understand anything?

02:07.136 --> 02:08.160
i came here

02:08.680 --> 02:11.599
Talk to you, if I can.

02:20.039 --> 02:22.599
Chengbi, you are actually a mute, right?

02:28.520 --> 02:30.700
My ex didn’t talk much;

02:30.700 --> 02:32.040
Almost like a mute.

02:32.040 --> 02:33.720
He goes home to visit his family

02:33.720 --> 02:34.800
and never came back,

02:35.439 --> 02:36.840
It's like he never existed.

03:02.400 --> 03:03.800
Were you the one who killed Mr. Song?

03:05.960 --> 03:07.439
Thank God.

03:08.960 --> 03:10.360
I hope he dies.

03:10.360 --> 03:12.159
There are knife marks there

03:12.680 --> 03:13.840
On Master Song's carriage.

03:17.560 --> 03:18.960
Not many people in the capital use blades.

03:19.719 --> 03:20.768
As for your blade,

03:21.759 --> 03:23.000
When you decide to use a blade

03:23.680 --> 03:25.560
Qingxing asked me to design it as a gift.

03:27.199 --> 03:28.719
I've modified it so it will be more

03:29.280 --> 03:31.479
It's suitable for women and
I can recognize it.

03:32.759 --> 03:34.920
My spies near the Prince Regent's residence have reported

03:34.920 --> 03:36.400
Someone broke into the mansion tonight.

03:37.248 --> 03:38.280
He Jiuling.

03:39.080 --> 03:40.680
He's yours too, isn't he?

03:42.479 --> 03:43.580
what do you want?

03:43.580 --> 03:45.620
Arrest me like before?

03:45.620 --> 03:47.380
if i want to do this

03:47.380 --> 03:48.759
I did this a long time ago.

03:50.199 --> 03:51.264
Are you playing with me?

03:52.199 --> 03:54.220
do you like seeing me

03:54.220 --> 03:55.319
Acting like a clown?

03:56.599 --> 03:57.840
If this is the case,

03:57.840 --> 03:59.600
There's no harm in killing you.

03:59.600 --> 04:01.919
He Jiuling, don’t you understand yet?

04:02.479 --> 04:05.399
No matter what you want to do, I can help you.

04:05.399 --> 04:06.520
help me?

04:07.680 --> 04:10.520
Your family is like Master Zhongyong’s watchdog
. help me?

04:13.152 --> 04:14.304
I am not my family

04:14.919 --> 04:16.480
I'm not a regent either.

04:17.279 --> 04:18.800
I'm just myself.

04:19.680 --> 04:20.839
I just want to atone for my sins.

04:22.639 --> 04:23.648
do it.

04:35.319 --> 04:36.384
Why did you stop?

04:37.079 --> 04:38.240
Do you think I'm scared?

04:40.720 --> 04:42.120
you know too.

04:42.120 --> 04:44.519
Whether it's you, me, or anyone else,

04:45.160 --> 04:47.160
At that time none of us had the ability

04:47.160 --> 04:48.940
We can't change the outcome,

04:48.940 --> 04:50.000
we can?

05:17.959 --> 05:20.560
Master, where are you going?

05:23.240 --> 05:26.620
Master, it's getting dark. where are you going?

05:26.620 --> 05:27.980
I can send someone to escort you.

05:27.980 --> 05:29.040
unnecessary.

05:36.079 --> 05:37.420
Don't bother, Your Highness.

05:37.420 --> 05:39.639
I can take care of the young master.

05:41.160 --> 05:45.000
Not bad, but it's too late

05:45.000 --> 05:47.000
There may be tigers and wolves outside the tent.

05:47.000 --> 05:49.839
You should be careful.

05:58.800 --> 05:59.808
I want to see

06:00.360 --> 06:01.959
Who wants to take my life away.

06:13.240 --> 06:15.079
Why are you
here alone in the middle of the night?

06:15.079 --> 06:17.160
What if something happens?

06:24.759 --> 06:26.600
My eyes are a bit red, aren't they?

06:26.600 --> 06:28.360
Maybe I'm just tired.

06:28.360 --> 06:29.940
this late,

06:29.940 --> 06:31.140
Then let's go back and rest.

06:31.140 --> 06:33.079
Tomorrow we must go to the hunting ground.

06:35.439 --> 06:36.448
tomorrow,

06:37.000 --> 06:38.176
Don't go to the hunting grounds.

06:38.959 --> 06:40.140
Did you forget it?

06:40.140 --> 06:41.680
The emperor gave me a bow and arrow

06:41.680 --> 06:44.439
And said he wanted to see me shoot a wild boar.

06:45.879 --> 06:46.976
Don't go.

06:50.519 --> 06:51.616
Alright alright.

06:52.319 --> 06:54.560
Do you want me to fly a kite with you?

06:55.279 --> 06:57.320
Then I will fly a kite with you tomorrow

06:57.320 --> 07:00.959
I'll teach you how to ride a horse.
The day after tomorrow I will...

07:00.959 --> 07:01.959
Don’t go the day after tomorrow either.

07:04.079 --> 07:06.560
Rong Yu, you...what's wrong with you?

07:10.079 --> 07:11.104
I'm not sure myself.

07:12.519 --> 07:14.160
But can you not go?

07:18.879 --> 07:20.440
You haven't told me yet,

07:20.440 --> 07:22.079
Why are you here alone?

07:24.680 --> 07:25.839
I'm afraid of uncle

07:26.680 --> 07:28.859
If he knew he would be angry with you

07:28.859 --> 07:30.500
You run around.

07:30.500 --> 07:32.160
He is an elder.

07:32.160 --> 07:33.860
if he is angry with me

07:33.860 --> 07:35.240
I won't take it seriously.

07:36.439 --> 07:38.940
Your family is my family.

07:38.940 --> 07:40.440
I will be nice to him

07:40.440 --> 07:43.160
I will try to make him forgive me.

08:05.199 --> 08:06.208
Good morning, Master.

08:08.600 --> 08:10.060
The lady said,

08:10.060 --> 08:12.400
You stay up late
and look at her before going to bed,

08:12.400 --> 08:13.920
So she told me not to wake you up.

08:14.600 --> 08:15.616
Where is she now?

08:15.616 --> 08:17.680
She was just called over

08:17.680 --> 08:20.220
The lady of the main palace,

08:20.220 --> 08:21.639
Now she should be called Princess Xihe.

08:23.840 --> 08:24.864
Master.

08:49.919 --> 08:50.919
Ms. Rong.

08:52.544 --> 08:53.600
Ms. Rong.

08:55.639 --> 08:56.879
Why don't you play a tune?

08:58.200 --> 09:00.440
Sorry, I don't know what to do.

09:00.440 --> 09:01.919
If nothing else

09:01.919 --> 09:02.919
I'll take my leave first

09:03.559 --> 09:04.608
wait,

09:07.919 --> 09:09.600
As a noble lady of the Jialin family,

09:09.600 --> 09:11.880
I don’t even understand this most basic skill

09:11.880 --> 09:13.960
It's so embarrassing.

09:13.960 --> 09:15.980
Our ancestor emperor
established a school for girls,

09:15.980 --> 09:19.900
Enable girls to become proficient in
poetry, music, and piano.

09:19.900 --> 09:21.099
Ms. Rong.

09:21.099 --> 09:22.460
You couldn't draw before.

09:22.460 --> 09:23.780
Now you can't play the guzheng.

09:23.780 --> 09:25.639
You have to be able to do something.

09:27.440 --> 09:29.540
Poetry, song, painting, music, and
pipa art.

09:29.540 --> 09:30.799
I can't do any of these things.

09:31.440 --> 09:32.879
So if there is any related incident

09:33.399 --> 09:34.820
Don't bother inviting me.

09:34.820 --> 09:36.800
If you don't know how, you can learn.

09:36.800 --> 09:39.800
The face of a woman
before she gets married is the face of her father and brothers.

09:39.800 --> 09:41.779
And after getting married, it becomes the face of the husband's family.

09:41.779 --> 09:44.600
Playing with swords is not
something that can be shown on the stage.

09:44.600 --> 09:47.008
Do you think you
will be drafted into war in the future?

09:47.776 --> 09:49.680
Since you live in the capital,

09:49.680 --> 09:52.160
At the ladies' party

09:52.160 --> 09:53.340
If there is nothing you can do,

09:53.340 --> 09:54.679
Don't you look like -

09:56.960 --> 09:58.016
Like a fool?

10:01.360 --> 10:03.080
Try to twist Mrs. Rong's hand a little.

10:04.000 --> 10:06.740
She was disabled for a while before her marriage.

10:06.740 --> 10:08.700
I wonder if she can still play the guzheng.

10:08.700 --> 10:11.039
If she can, I, as a princess, will definitely help her.

10:11.679 --> 10:14.220
After the hunting trip,
I will arrange for her to study

10:14.220 --> 10:15.399
and my six or seven year old cousin.

10:16.639 --> 10:18.520
Poetry, song, painting, music,
pipa art

10:18.520 --> 10:19.820
Like swords and clubs,

10:19.820 --> 10:21.520
Spears, axes, hooks and forks.

10:21.520 --> 10:23.000
There is no difference in their value.

10:23.919 --> 10:26.624
What kind of person does a woman want to be?

10:26.624 --> 10:28.320
Who is criticizing.

10:29.320 --> 10:31.480
As for
the face of my father and my husband’s family,

10:32.440 --> 10:34.600
Why don't they make their own money?

10:35.679 --> 10:36.919
But is it up to you?

10:38.639 --> 10:39.639
What will we do?

10:40.160 --> 10:41.240
They immediately started fighting.

10:41.240 --> 10:42.279
indeed.

10:42.879 --> 10:44.300
they do not

10:44.300 --> 10:46.240
It was very honorable yesterday.

10:47.519 --> 10:48.879
Others deliberately let you win.

10:49.984 --> 10:51.060
Did they do it?

10:51.060 --> 10:52.416
What?

10:54.360 --> 10:56.544
Let it go, I'm a princess now.

10:57.056 --> 10:58.120
I dare you to disrespect me.

10:58.120 --> 11:00.840
Yesterday I told them what dignity means.

11:01.440 --> 11:04.799
It means don't be
arrogant and make others uncomfortable.

11:05.360 --> 11:07.020
If you don't understand this,

11:07.020 --> 11:08.380
I wouldn't mind teaching you again.

11:08.380 --> 11:10.039
Just like you taught me
how to play guzheng today.

11:10.639 --> 11:12.180
let go. Let me go.

11:12.180 --> 11:13.600
Mrs. Rong, you...

11:14.279 --> 11:17.000
I just want to drink tea alone with Miss Jiang

11:17.000 --> 11:18.699
Solve the problem

11:18.699 --> 11:20.700
She is always unhappy to see me.

11:20.700 --> 11:22.848
If you want to play the guzheng, come on.

11:22.848 --> 11:23.960
I…

11:24.800 --> 11:25.960
how…

11:26.519 --> 11:27.900
I advise you to behave yourself.

11:27.900 --> 11:29.320
In front of so many people,

11:29.320 --> 11:31.120
Don't lose your dignity as a princess.

11:32.800 --> 11:33.824
wait.

11:34.879 --> 11:36.480
The emperor and regent are here.

11:36.480 --> 11:38.880
He Jiuling wouldn't do anything to her.

11:39.680 --> 11:41.240
But if you offend her

11:41.240 --> 11:42.739
She definitely won't mind

11:42.739 --> 11:44.240
Create a scene for others to laugh at.

11:46.879 --> 11:48.000
Chengbi.

11:52.480 --> 11:53.840
She drank some hallucinogenic tea,

11:54.559 --> 11:56.799
But the effect only lasts
for one stick of incense.

11:57.399 --> 11:58.880
I'll be back in time.

11:58.880 --> 11:59.959
Keep an eye on her.

11:59.959 --> 12:01.024
Be careful.

12:06.799 --> 12:08.519
Master.

12:09.120 --> 12:11.159
Why are you so anxious to find her?

12:11.680 --> 12:12.704
The place is full of women.

12:12.704 --> 12:13.824
Master Rong.

12:13.824 --> 12:14.912
Let's not stay here, okay?

12:14.912 --> 12:16.020
Isn't this Master Rong?

12:16.020 --> 12:17.984
Master,
what might happen to your lady?

12:18.624 --> 12:19.744
Master.

12:20.440 --> 12:21.472
Master Rong.

12:22.320 --> 12:24.240
Is Mr. Rong looking for He Jiuling?

12:27.200 --> 12:28.660
He Jiuling and Princess Xihe

12:28.660 --> 12:29.960
Has been gone for a while.

12:34.039 --> 12:35.240
Master, Master.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.480
Master, where are you going?

12:37.840 --> 12:38.976
Master.

13:23.039 --> 13:24.064
wait.

13:48.879 --> 13:49.879
Master.

13:50.399 --> 13:51.559
What are you doing?

13:56.000 --> 13:57.080
Your Highness,

13:57.080 --> 13:58.719
Your Majesty gave you a new horse today,

13:58.719 --> 13:59.979
The young master also comes to try it.

13:59.979 --> 14:01.200
Try horses?

14:04.768 --> 14:05.888
Master,

14:06.480 --> 14:07.680
This is a hunting ground.

14:07.680 --> 14:09.159
There are wild animals around,

14:09.159 --> 14:10.699
The sword has no eyes.

14:10.699 --> 14:12.240
I don't want you to get hurt.

14:13.559 --> 14:16.519
Master, Master.

14:20.704 --> 14:21.824
It's noisy.

14:25.559 --> 14:27.000
For your safety,

14:27.520 --> 14:30.019
I will send someone to take you back.

14:30.019 --> 14:31.168
Servants!

14:32.960 --> 14:35.039
Yesterday, His Majesty
granted me a new position.

14:35.039 --> 14:36.419
so what?

14:36.419 --> 14:37.480
It's higher than yours.

15:40.039 --> 15:41.279
Your Highness.

15:41.279 --> 15:43.000
Can you slow down a little?

15:43.000 --> 15:44.959
My master is not a skilled rider,

15:44.959 --> 15:46.000
He could barely keep up.

15:54.759 --> 15:57.320
Your Highness, why did you stop?

15:57.320 --> 15:59.919
My master's Turkish horse could hardly move.

16:06.399 --> 16:07.456
Your Highness,

16:07.456 --> 16:09.120
Why are you running so fast again?

16:09.120 --> 16:10.799
My master couldn't keep up.

16:25.000 --> 16:26.080
The Prince Regent is back.

16:26.960 --> 16:29.960
I'm here to count the games for His Highness.

16:30.559 --> 16:31.799
Just now, several lords came back

16:31.799 --> 16:33.360
There are only a few chickens.

16:33.360 --> 16:35.159
And His Majesty also had a great time.

16:36.919 --> 16:38.639
I have nothing here, go away.

17:00.559 --> 17:01.600
Wipe your drool.

17:06.039 --> 17:07.839
I'm not drooling. You are fooling me.

17:11.200 --> 17:12.400
Well, I must have read it wrong.

17:14.039 --> 17:16.000
Sorry, I fell asleep while I was scolding you.

17:16.799 --> 17:17.860
However, judging from your situation

17:17.860 --> 17:19.880
sincerely apologize,

17:20.519 --> 17:21.920
I don't blame you just yet.

17:24.759 --> 17:26.380
This is the illusion you see.

17:26.380 --> 17:27.488
What did you say?

17:29.200 --> 17:30.304
there is nothing.

17:33.319 --> 17:34.720
Cheng Bi, let’s go.

17:36.319 --> 17:38.540
She was scolded severely by me just now.

17:38.540 --> 17:41.160
Why does a paper tiger act so tough?

17:44.559 --> 17:45.880
So refreshing.

17:50.160 --> 17:51.359
Why am I here?

18:17.312 --> 18:18.360
Rong Yu.

18:18.360 --> 18:19.519
slower.

18:19.519 --> 18:20.880
I don't run.

18:22.119 --> 18:24.359
Rong Yu, be careful not to fall.

19:06.920 --> 19:08.720
where have you been?

19:11.440 --> 19:14.319
I just had tea with the ladies.

19:15.039 --> 19:17.000
Nothing to worry about, right?

19:17.680 --> 19:18.688
Really?

19:19.920 --> 19:22.119
What? Do not you trust me?

19:23.400 --> 19:25.280
Instead, you're running around all day.

19:25.280 --> 19:27.839
Do you know how dangerous this is?

19:31.039 --> 19:33.519
Forget it, I'll find another chance later.

20:31.480 --> 20:34.160
Jiuling, come back and sleep.

21:09.680 --> 21:10.839
Do you want this?

21:19.000 --> 21:20.096
how about this?

21:25.480 --> 21:26.640
Eat more of this

21:26.640 --> 21:27.760
Rong Yu,

21:27.760 --> 21:30.039
Do you know
how angry I get these days?

21:33.279 --> 21:35.039
I don't know what to do with you.

21:36.720 --> 21:37.824
Frankly speaking.

21:37.824 --> 21:40.039
Are you sent by God to punish me?

21:50.200 --> 21:52.100
Have some tea.

21:52.100 --> 21:53.920
Follow the regent all day long,

21:53.920 --> 21:54.960
are not you tired?

21:56.079 --> 21:57.720
what are you saying?

22:01.359 --> 22:02.359
there is nothing.

22:05.319 --> 22:06.880
What's there to argue with you?

22:08.064 --> 22:09.080
Let’s order more food

22:09.080 --> 22:10.960
This Li Yuhan still dares to play the piano?

22:11.480 --> 22:13.600
Everyone was gossiping the day before yesterday

22:13.600 --> 22:16.040
She plays the piano out of tune,

22:16.040 --> 22:18.360
She should
restrain here, lift there.

22:18.360 --> 22:19.860
so embarrassing

22:19.860 --> 22:22.300
She puts on her best face

22:22.300 --> 22:24.079
Look down on everyone.

22:24.680 --> 22:26.519
Finally someone looked down on her.

22:26.519 --> 22:27.584
Exactly.

22:28.128 --> 22:29.260
Speaking of which,

22:29.260 --> 22:30.600
Mr. Rong’s piano skills

22:30.600 --> 22:31.920
All extremely beautiful.

22:32.640 --> 22:34.119
It's a pity now.

22:35.200 --> 22:36.256
it's a pity.

22:37.160 --> 22:38.200
Have some tea.

22:40.279 --> 22:42.079
Have you ever played guzheng before?

22:43.920 --> 22:46.199
Are you talking about what we're hearing now?

22:46.199 --> 22:48.340
I think she sounds horrible.

22:48.340 --> 22:49.720
She even missed some notes.

22:54.079 --> 22:56.119
Maybe I'll do better.

22:59.559 --> 23:00.840
Even if you can,

23:00.840 --> 23:03.039
I don’t know when I’ll actually hear it.

23:03.839 --> 23:05.799
Master, madam.

23:08.519 --> 23:09.536
During these days of hunting,

23:09.536 --> 23:10.800
Your Majesty got some good stuff

23:10.800 --> 23:12.140
and are distributing them.

23:12.140 --> 23:14.320
Everyone else is gone,
but you are nowhere to be seen

23:14.320 --> 23:17.880
So I've been sent to invite you
to claim your reward.

23:18.880 --> 23:19.880
thank you, sir.

23:22.880 --> 23:24.839
sorry. I've never been able
to get a military badge.

23:27.880 --> 23:29.119
This wasn't supposed to be an easy task.

23:30.599 --> 23:31.680
Apart from,

23:32.759 --> 23:34.960
Everyone else was looking at the Regent's Palace.

23:41.920 --> 23:42.960
Master,

23:42.960 --> 23:44.400
Isn't this bunny cute?

23:44.400 --> 23:46.176
Look, it's been hungry for a while.

23:46.944 --> 23:48.759
Come on, come on, feed it quickly.

24:00.759 --> 24:02.100
Watchers outside the Prince Regent's palace

24:02.100 --> 24:03.200
It was sent by Yan Lie.

24:03.839 --> 24:04.840
I was at the hunting ground a few days ago,

24:04.840 --> 24:06.160
He even offered to help me.

24:07.200 --> 24:08.680
In order to stop that old gangster,

24:09.559 --> 24:11.319
I have been supporting the Yan family
to fight against him.

24:12.480 --> 24:14.640
I've egged him on many times

24:15.480 --> 24:17.359
This has made him
suspicious of the Yan family.

24:19.000 --> 24:20.300
Steal military signs

24:20.300 --> 24:21.800
It had alarmed him.

24:21.800 --> 24:24.679
If he discovers that Yan Lie is spying on
the Regent's Palace,

24:24.679 --> 24:26.319
Despite Yan Li’s intentions,

24:26.920 --> 24:28.519
The Yan family will be in danger.

24:30.279 --> 24:31.279
it's a pity.

24:34.759 --> 24:36.096
If Your Majesty wants to use Yan Lie,

24:36.832 --> 24:37.920
After this incident,

24:38.496 --> 24:39.920
You can put him under your command.

24:42.240 --> 24:44.119
But what you hate the most is the Yan family.

24:46.559 --> 24:47.759
I still.

24:53.519 --> 24:55.200
But I've learned to understand

24:55.839 --> 24:57.440
meaning no choice

24:59.079 --> 25:00.599
When things change unpredictably.

25:02.240 --> 25:05.039
I also learned how to survive hatred.

25:07.359 --> 25:08.759
Don't push yourself too hard.

25:10.359 --> 25:11.400
regardless,

25:12.319 --> 25:14.799
Things are much better now than before.

25:15.960 --> 25:18.480
I'm counting on you to solve
a lot of problems.

25:20.519 --> 25:22.260
you must protect yourself

25:22.260 --> 25:23.519
And be very careful.

25:26.240 --> 25:27.424
Understood.

25:29.599 --> 25:30.680
By the way, He Jiuling,

25:32.200 --> 25:33.480
Now like this with Rong Yu,

25:34.960 --> 25:36.279
Isn't this too difficult for you?

25:38.720 --> 25:39.759
he?

25:41.799 --> 25:43.440
He might actually be my lucky star.

25:44.960 --> 25:46.600
If you want to leave him in the future

25:46.600 --> 25:47.640
I can help you.

25:49.799 --> 25:51.119
When the He family encountered misfortune,

25:52.559 --> 25:54.319
He saved me from water and fire.

25:55.079 --> 25:56.480
I know you are a
person who takes kindness seriously.

25:57.359 --> 25:59.079
But also keep this in mind.

26:00.079 --> 26:01.400
You never know when you'll need it.

26:09.088 --> 26:16.256
【Rong's Mansion】

26:30.720 --> 26:31.780
The people from the pharmacy just came over.

26:31.780 --> 26:33.664
They said they found ambrosia.

26:34.240 --> 26:35.240
Where?

26:35.240 --> 26:36.416
Outside the city, inside Jingshan Mountain.

26:38.599 --> 26:39.712
That's a long way off.

26:41.359 --> 26:43.920
It doesn't matter.
No matter how far I have to go.

27:00.000 --> 27:01.880
Why can't I see
a future for the Regent?

27:03.079 --> 27:04.759
Even the stars are blurred.

27:06.559 --> 27:08.400
There aren't any useful clues.

27:09.440 --> 27:10.799
How is this going?

27:12.920 --> 27:16.220
Could it be that there are masters around him
who are changing his destiny?

27:16.220 --> 27:17.480
I know nothing about this?

27:18.920 --> 27:20.000
Master.

27:20.512 --> 27:21.536
It's getting late.

27:21.536 --> 27:23.360
Don't you need to buy lotus cakes for Madam?

27:23.904 --> 27:25.240
If you don't go now, they'll be sold out.

28:25.880 --> 28:28.400
You came back later than usual today.

28:34.160 --> 28:35.200
They are still hot.

28:36.200 --> 28:38.480
The future will always be hot.

28:39.319 --> 28:40.400
It doesn't matter.

28:40.400 --> 28:42.799
I just said it casually.

28:43.559 --> 28:44.680
It tastes better when hot.

28:49.720 --> 28:52.079
It’s even more delicious than what you like to eat in Xicheng.

28:55.160 --> 28:56.160
Isn't it?

28:58.160 --> 28:59.599
Eat more if you like.

29:05.039 --> 29:06.080
By the way, Rong Yu,

29:07.359 --> 29:09.319
I have something to discuss with you.

29:10.039 --> 29:11.720
I need to find an herb

29:12.400 --> 29:14.079
It's called ambrosia.

29:14.079 --> 29:16.540
It's freshest after it rains.

29:16.540 --> 29:18.380
So if it rains tonight

29:18.380 --> 29:20.039
I'm going to Jingshan.

29:20.599 --> 29:23.519
This way I can get up early
to get the medicine tomorrow.

29:27.872 --> 29:28.896
hurry up.

29:30.960 --> 29:32.032
let's go.

29:33.519 --> 29:35.400
I brought you some summer clothes.

29:35.920 --> 29:37.440
If the weather is hot tomorrow

29:37.960 --> 29:39.599
Let Zhanping change it for you.

29:40.400 --> 29:41.540
And this sachet,

29:41.540 --> 29:42.759
I just did it,

29:43.440 --> 29:44.660
And the smell is a bit strong,

29:44.660 --> 29:46.599
But it is used to repel mosquitoes.

29:47.359 --> 29:49.860
Even if you think
it smells bad when you sleep at night,

29:49.860 --> 29:51.640
Never take it off.

29:52.519 --> 29:54.959
I also smoked your quilt with vanilla.

29:54.959 --> 29:56.039
How long will you be gone?

29:57.880 --> 29:58.960
I'll be back tomorrow night.

30:02.839 --> 30:04.512
It's just one day.

30:04.512 --> 30:06.112
nothing to worry about

30:06.784 --> 30:07.872
correct?

30:15.519 --> 30:17.960
But I still felt uneasy.

30:22.240 --> 30:23.519
Then I'll go with you.

30:24.640 --> 30:26.319
That would make me more worried.

30:27.160 --> 30:28.460
Rong Yu, Rong Yu.

30:28.460 --> 30:31.160
This annoying
habit of dragging things out of me

30:31.160 --> 30:32.720
it was all your fault.

30:33.480 --> 30:35.100
you are too much trouble

30:35.100 --> 30:36.352
It's too worrying.

30:37.160 --> 30:38.279
I've never

30:39.039 --> 30:40.160
Like before.

30:41.960 --> 30:42.960
My fault.

30:44.000 --> 30:46.400
This is. I blame you.

30:48.640 --> 30:49.640
But this time,

30:50.400 --> 30:52.160
Let me go with you.

30:54.839 --> 30:56.992
All right. I heard.

30:57.728 --> 31:01.160
Don't worry, Chengbi and Wu Ritan are by my side.

31:01.759 --> 31:02.816
when you come back,

31:03.440 --> 31:04.759
We will move to another house.

31:15.559 --> 31:16.680
it seems

31:17.839 --> 31:19.720
I have a family again.

34:20.159 --> 34:21.300
Tan, slow down.

34:21.300 --> 34:22.900
We have collected all the medicines.

34:22.900 --> 34:25.119
Just because we have it
, we are afraid of losing its efficacy.

34:25.960 --> 34:27.300
Also, take a look at yourself.

34:27.300 --> 34:29.119
You obviously
want to get back to the city more than anyone else.

34:33.000 --> 34:34.920
I'll get some water. You guys keep eating

34:35.679 --> 34:36.840
Keep an eye out for herbs.

34:45.960 --> 34:47.000
These are the Regent's men.

34:52.719 --> 34:54.639
Traveling with so few people

34:55.159 --> 34:56.639
It's really too perverted.

34:59.360 --> 35:00.719
After what happened to the Yan family,

35:01.480 --> 35:03.119
I don't really trust the people

35:03.960 --> 35:05.519
All around me now.

35:06.199 --> 35:08.519
Who knows when they will betray me?

35:09.199 --> 35:12.679
Now the Chen family
wants to go to Yanzhou

35:13.599 --> 35:15.800
Yan State has been demoted to Shu,

35:15.800 --> 35:17.020
i have no plan

35:17.020 --> 35:19.520
No more promotion of left and right generals.

35:19.520 --> 35:20.960
It's safer to keep everything

35:20.960 --> 35:23.679
In my own hands.

35:24.400 --> 35:26.800
And, in the hunting grounds,

35:26.800 --> 35:29.740
I had the distinct feeling that someone
was trying to hurt me.

35:29.740 --> 35:31.920
The Yan family also began
to oppose me frequently.

35:32.440 --> 35:35.719
