35:36.480 --> 35:39.680
I really don't know what to do.

35:39.680 --> 35:43.320
Sir, is it possible that your divination is wrong?

35:43.320 --> 35:44.416
impossible.

35:45.088 --> 35:47.584
The only mistake was including Rong Yu.

35:47.584 --> 35:48.720
This voice...

35:48.720 --> 35:50.719
The fate of people related to astrology
is unpredictable.

35:51.440 --> 35:52.660
His appearance must be

35:52.660 --> 35:54.640
Interact with events at the Hunting Ground.

35:54.640 --> 35:56.480
If I could use a star map

35:56.480 --> 35:58.599
I will be able to predict more things.

36:09.440 --> 36:10.880
I understand.

36:12.719 --> 36:15.760
I need to seek more advice from Lord Yung

36:15.760 --> 36:17.559
To keep me and my family safe.

36:18.176 --> 36:19.200
certainly.

36:19.808 --> 36:22.559
As long as I am regent,

36:23.079 --> 36:25.920
Whatever you need, just ask.

36:26.519 --> 36:28.000
Not to mention the He family,

36:28.000 --> 36:29.199
Even if there are two or three,

36:29.719 --> 36:31.000
If they dare stand in my way

36:31.000 --> 36:32.079
